documentation.description:
`enabled(a)` is true when the action `a` is enabled in the current state.
An action is enabled when all its preconditions are satisfied.

# Examples

```
var x: int
action Init = x' = 0
action Under10 = all {
  x < 10,
  x' = x + 1,
}
action Over10 = all {
  x >= 10,
  x' = x + 1,
}
temporal Property = always(or {  
  x < 10 and enabled(Under10),
  x >= 10 and enabled(Over10), 
})
```
